                                <opener>
                                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Babelsberg</hi></placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1945-08-01">August 1,
                                            1945</date>.]</dateline>
                                </opener>
                                <p rend="center"><hi rend="smallcaps">Third Report of the Economic
                                        Subcommittee to the Foreign Ministers</hi></p>
                                <p rend="center">. . . . . . . . . . . . . .</p>
                                <p>The Soviet representatives reported that they were not yet in a
                                    position further to discuss the matter of oil supplies from the
                                        East.<note n="2" xml:id="d1325fn2">See <ref target="#d1320">document No. 1320</ref>.</note></p>
